o:comment: An organization identifier as defined in ISO 6523(-1). Note that many existing organization identifiers such as [leiCode](https://schema.org/leiCode), [duns](https://schema.org/duns) and [vatID](https://schema.org/vatID) can be expressed as an ISO 6523 identifier by setting the ICD part of the ISO 6523 identifier accordingly.
o:label: iso6523Code
